  "about": "Tima is a robot designed to look like Duke Red's deceased daughter. On the outset, she has no memory of who she is or what her purpose is. She is helped by a boy named Kenichi and is taken through Metropolis. She sees all of the troubles in the world through her eyes and finally discovers her destiny, much to her chagrin. In a release of anger, she sets out to destroy all that has troubled her.",
